{"tid":1436946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實警察當我地曱甴呢件事一定要全世界都知","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:45:13.000Z","uid":2002,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"625887898a3f40c0b6d345387e1869acfd95b5fe","tid":1436946,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"你會發現而家有一班企圖標籤污衊示威者, 不斷宣揚仇恨, 甚至用作警察濫權的藉口, 企圖支持極權統治, 令香港成為警察國家...<br />\n<br />\n&quot;二戰時期的猶太人受到納粹的迫害，當時把猶太人物化為「蝨子」或「寄生蟲」。猶太人經過種族標籤化之後，把他們予以區隔，讓他們成為敵人，同時提供屠殺一個合理的解釋。&quot;<br />\n&quot;大屠殺發生在1994年位於東非的盧旺達，是胡圖族人對圖西族人進行的盧安達大屠殺，胡圖族極端分子對圖西族人的蔑稱『蟑螂』&quot;<br />\n&quot;警員佐級協會林志偉指責「這些暴徒不能以人相稱，亦不能以畜相稱，如此低等之物只能以昆蟲中最怕見光的種類來稱呼─『蟑螂』」。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次次大屠殺前都會咁叫對家示威者<br />\n而定好撚驚會唔會當我地唔係人咁射殺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook cap晒d圖 做文宣<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野應該真係核彈級文宣"},{"pid":"3b16a37eeb2fca085207e16f3b9c546ccdf33638","tid":1436946,"uid":81319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"721e5093ddc511bcfb7ffd50848644c7128af9be","tid":1436946,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f08365944cbe1cc800b5a5ef31b1a4a5a972ce1a","tid":1436946,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a021573be59e9c5bd95e3ce50982013c49dba73","tid":1436946,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Omgzz5p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmgzz5p.png&h=1f0bcb4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTtFvDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTtFvDL.png&h=77e7ccad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkuYhiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkuYhiM.png&h=ea39bd92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb464ab50d28a9